{"tid":654903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【割地兩檢】馬時亨：唔好阻住地球轉","createTime":"2018-05-06T05:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T13:44:42.000Z","uid":150685,"like":5,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6e35a542e744e1fc298add7afe629f72ba6bff8c","tid":654903,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180506/large/1525575737_bc91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180506%2Flarge%2F1525575737_bc91.png&h=d2236075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵主席馬時亨出席電台節目時表示，如果一地兩檢草案未能於在本立法年度通過，高鐵將不能如期在今年9月通車。他呼籲議員不要再拖延審議進度，「唔好阻住地球轉」。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨稱明白政治很多時候都是一種表態，而議員亦可就一地兩檢作出表態：「<span style=\"color: red;\">你可以表個態，但唔好阻住地球轉囉</span>！」他希望議員要以大局為重：「<span style=\"color: red;\">政治好多嘢都係表個態之嘛，你明知你都未必夠票</span>。」他又指泛民議員明知不夠票仍繼續嘗試拖延，「拖極始終會通過」。對於港鐵至今仍未與政府簽訂營運協議，馬時亨表示，仍有一些商業細節要商討，他強調港鐵非「獅子開大口」，有信心能在通車前完成所有程序。<br />\n<br />\n上月廣深港香港段高鐵列車「動感號」試行曾發生出軌事故，馬時亨強調目前已進行相關工作並會重新試行，對能如期通車有信心。他預料通車初期多人會試搭，相信客量會較多。而營運初期將安排較多短途的班次，如前往往潮州、福建、武漢、長沙等，他引述中國鐵路總公司指，前往北京、上海等長途線，不少人都會選乘飛機，因此不會安排太多班次。<br />\n<br />\n早前馬時亨曾提倡於廣州高鐵站附近建「香港城」，他解釋高鐵開通後，港人可選擇於香港工作但居於內地，交通費將以價格較便宜的「月票」解決。他又稱「香港城」將會有不少配套令港人感舒適，「用較少的價錢住好一點」。他又強調自己只是提供意見，希望能解決問題，否認自己有「任務要推銷」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180506/58158201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180506%2F58158201&d=sGwUIirdB4qypkm10ixhJjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2affbc86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180506%2F58158201&h=d944f903\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180506/58158201</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9vNIQDDimPY/U3bn7t0pVYI/AAAAAAAACw4/iUfSIXalfFM/s1600/20140512_NewsEastWest.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-9vNIQDDimPY%2FU3bn7t0pVYI%2FAAAAAAAACw4%2FiUfSIXalfFM%2Fs1600%2F20140512_NewsEastWest.jpg&h=6886d0dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1624b48136bfccc092516d288fb6036ffd38ad60","tid":654903,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8004ea5c0c27d51bef20df2aa256618927cf2da","tid":654903,"uid":16676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:07:26.000Z","msg":"一言堂 <br />\n當正自己係土皇帝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f2be753aa0b1df34f28670ffbd4399a58a3986","tid":654903,"uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"仲要個垃圾會黎做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e6451e366e059d60ad6748fee3955643135415","tid":654903,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:33:22.000Z","msg":"我大曬"},{"pid":"aacb9620c36fc5a16f4c0a8edae3f00c0b2d6cf0","tid":654903,"uid":103936,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"俾人老強果時<br />\n女人唔夠男人大力丫嘛<br />\n始終會俾人強姦到嘛<br />\n咪撚反抗喇<br />\n「你可以表個態，但唔好阻住地球轉囉！」<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efc1edd938db8625680f5b3ecea8867a922537e","tid":654903,"uid":146621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:46:38.000Z","msg":"語言偽術都廢事講<br />\nEQ 又低<br />\n咁都做到咁高位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed6f29ff298d8c81d8953d79e11931c6a1cda6d","tid":654903,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1404ac25b0fb9dcc1a801fd34d58e2c835cc925e","tid":654903,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:48:44.000